text: Jesús López may refer to: * Jesús López (weightlifter) (born 1984), Venezuelan weightlifter * Jesús López de Lara (1892–?), Spanish fencer * Jesús López Pacheco (1930–1997), novelist, translator, poet and professor of Spanish * Jesús López Cobos (1940–2018), Spanish conductor * Jesús Francisco López (born 1997), Mexican footballer
title: Jesús López
